			<img
				src="/images/filter.jpg"
				alt="JustCook app interface"
				width="400"
				height="800"
			/>
		</div>
		<div class="solution-content">
			<h3>JustCook.app Concept</h3>
			<p>
				A hybrid platform where users can browse dynamic,
				portrait-oriented food content and seamlessly order meal
